---
<section class="relative z-20 bg-[#6A0DAD] text-white overflow-hidden py-24 lg:py-32">
    <!-- Decorative SVG pattern background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.04] z-0"
         style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, white 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;">
    </div>

    <!-- Stroke Draw: Arc frame for CTA -->
    <svg data-index-draw class="absolute top-[50%] left-[3%] -translate-y-1/2 w-40 h-40 lg:w-56 lg:h-56 pointer-events-none z-0 hidden lg:block" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none">
        <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="90" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.2)" stroke-width="1.2" class="draw-path" />
        <path d="M100 15 A85 85 0 0 1 185 100" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.35)" stroke-width="1.8" class="draw-path" />
        <path d="M100 185 A85 85 0 0 1 15 100" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.35)" stroke-width="1.8" class="draw-path" />
    </svg>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1800px] px-6 sm:px-12 z-10">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="lg:col-span-6 relative">
                <div class="text-xs sm:text-sm md:text-base lg:text-xs font-mono text-purple-200 tracking-widest mb-6 reveal-text">
                    [ PRÓXIMO PASO ]
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-6xl 2xl:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] reveal-text">
                    ¿LISTO PARA <br>
                    <span class="text-purple-200">CONSTRUIR?</span>
                </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="lg:col-span-6 flex flex-col items-start lg:items-end justify-center">
                <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-purple-100 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-xl mb-10 reveal-text lg:text-right">
                    Hablemos de tu negocio y descubramos cómo podemos llevarlo al siguiente nivel con ingeniería digital a medida.
                </p>
                <div class="reveal-text">
                    <a href="/contact" data-cursor-text="INICIAR" class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 2xl:px-10 2xl:py-5 bg-white text-[#6A0DAD] font-bold rounded-full overflow-hidden transition-transform hover:scale-105">
                        <span class="relative z-10 group-hover:text-purple-900 transition-colors 2xl:text-lg">Iniciar Proyecto</span>
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 2xl:w-5 2xl:h-5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>